			"id": "b343ea29-7477-405b-b8d9-0128e3210eaf",
			"note": "<div><br></div>Rewrite the the systems of linear equations from above as matrix equations... thus motivating the idea of matrix multiplication.&nbsp;<br><br>Extend idea of matrix multiplication to matrix with more than one column.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div><div>Write down a couple of general \"matrix equations\" at random, but don't say anything about how/what the solutions are. &nbsp;Just ask questions, e.g., how many solutions? &nbsp;What do they look like?</div></div><div><br></div>"
